---
// src/components/AuthorProfile.astro
---
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="avatar-container" id="author-avatar-btn" title="点击查看关于我">
            <img src="/avatar.jpg" alt="OKay" class="hero-avatar interactive-avatar">
            <div class="avatar-hover-hint">关于我</div>
        </div>
        <h1>Hi，我是 <span class="text-accent">OKay</span> 👋</h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">专注智能硬件、嵌入式系统与电子产品设计<br>立志成为一名专业的智能硬件工程师</p>
        <div class="hero-tags">
            <span>智能硬件</span><span>嵌入式系统</span><span>电子产品设计</span><span>Linux</span><span>驱动开发</span><span>硬件调试</span><span>PCB设计</span><span>原理图设计</span><span>设备树</span><span>U-Boot</span><span>BSP适配</span><span>物联网</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Author Intro Modal -->
<div class="author-modal-overlay" id="author-modal">
    <div class="author-modal-content">
        <button class="modal-close-btn" id="modal-close-btn">
            <span class="material-icons-round">close</span>
        </button>
        <div class="modal-header">
            <img src="/avatar.jpg" alt="OKay" class="modal-avatar">
            <h2>OKay</h2>
            <p class="modal-subtitle">智能硬件开发者 / 嵌入式系统工程实践者</p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
            <p>你好！我是 OKay，一名专注于智能硬件、嵌入式系统和电子产品设计的工程师。</p>
            <p>目前我主要围绕以下方向持续积累与输出：</p>
            <ul>
                <li>⚡ <strong>智能硬件开发：</strong> 从需求分析、器件选型到原理图设计、PCB 实现和样机调试。</li>
                <li>🐧 <strong>嵌入式系统实践：</strong> 涵盖 U-Boot、Linux 内核、设备树、驱动开发与 BSP 适配。</li>
                <li>🔧 <strong>整机联调落地：</strong> 关注传感器接入、接口通信、系统稳定性和产品化验证。</li>
            </ul>
            <p>我会在这里持续记录项目经验、问题定位过程和设计思考，朝着专业的智能硬件工程师目标稳步前进，也期待与你一起交流成长。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
            <a href="https://github.com/OKayJH" target="_blank" class="modal-social-link">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"></path></svg>
                GitHub
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .avatar-container {
        position: relative;
        display: inline-block;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .interactive-avatar {
        transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275), box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .avatar-container:hover .interactive-avatar {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.3);
    }
    .avatar-hover-hint {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -10px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        background: var(--text-main);
        color: var(--bg-main);
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        padding: 4px 8px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease, bottom 0.3s ease;
        pointer-events: none;
        white-space: nowrap;
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    .avatar-container:hover .avatar-hover-hint {
        opacity: 1;
        bottom: -5px;
    }

    /* Modal Styles */
    .author-modal-overlay {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100vw;
        height: 100vh;
        padding: 16px;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        z-index: 1000;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        opacity: 0;
        visibility: hidden;
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease, visibility 0.3s ease;
    }
    .author-modal-overlay.active {
        opacity: 1;
        visibility: visible;
    }
    .author-modal-content {
        background: var(--bg-secondary);
        width: min(92vw, 500px);
        max-height: min(86vh, 720px);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: clamp(20px, 5vw, 40px);
        position: relative;
        transform: translateY(30px) scale(0.95);
        transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        overflow-y: auto;
    }
    .author-modal-overlay.active .author-modal-content {
        transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    }
    .modal-close-btn {
        position: absolute;
        top: 20px;
        right: 20px;
        background: var(--bg-tertiary);
        border: none;
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        cursor: pointer;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    .modal-close-btn:hover {
        background: var(--bg-hover);
        color: var(--text-main);
        transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
    .modal-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .modal-avatar {
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        border: 3px solid var(--border-light);
    }
    .modal-header h2 {
        margin: 0 0 4px 0;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .modal-subtitle {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .modal-body {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .modal-body p {
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .modal-body ul {
        margin: 0 0 16px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .modal-body li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .modal-body strong {
        color: var(--text-main);
    }
    .modal-footer {
        margin-top: 32px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        padding-top: 24px;
    }
    .modal-social-link {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        background: var(--bg-main);
        color: var(--text-main);
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    }
    .modal-social-link:hover {
        border-color: var(--accent);
        color: var(--accent);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .author-modal-overlay {
            padding: 12px;
        }
        .modal-avatar {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
        }
        .modal-header h2 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        .modal-body {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .modal-social-link {
            width: 100%;
            justify-content: center;
        }
    }
</style>

<script>
    document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', () => {
        const avatarBtn = document.getElementById('author-avatar-btn');
        const modal = document.getElementById('author-modal');
        const closeBtn = document.getElementById('modal-close-btn');

        if(avatarBtn && modal && closeBtn) {
            // Use cloned nodes to clear any old listeners
            const clonedBtn = avatarBtn.cloneNode(true);
            avatarBtn.parentNode.replaceChild(clonedBtn, avatarBtn);
            
            const clonedClose = closeBtn.cloneNode(true);
            closeBtn.parentNode.replaceChild(clonedClose, closeBtn);

            // Open modal
            clonedBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                modal.classList.add('active');
                document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden'; // Prevent background scrolling
            });

            // Close modal via button
            clonedClose.addEventListener('click', () => {
                modal.classList.remove('active');
                document.body.style.overflow = '';
            });

            // Clean up old window handler for Escape key if exists
            if (window._authorModalKeyHandler) {
                document.removeEventListener('keydown', window._authorModalKeyHandler);
            }
            window._authorModalKeyHandler = (e) => {
                if(e.key === 'Escape' && modal.classList.contains('active')) {
                    modal.classList.remove('active');
                    document.body.style.overflow = '';
                }
            };
            document.addEventListener('keydown', window._authorModalKeyHandler);

            // Close modal via overlay click - need to handle previous listeners
            const clonedModal = modal.cloneNode(true);
            modal.parentNode.replaceChild(clonedModal, modal);
            
            clonedModal.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                if (e.target === clonedModal) {
                    clonedModal.classList.remove('active');
                    document.body.style.overflow = '';
                }
            });
            
            // Re-assign references after cloning for the keydown handler to work later
            window._authorModalElement = clonedModal;
        }
    });
</script>
